Edwige Feuillère https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edwige_Feuill%C3%A8re 0 Edwige Feuillère (29 October 1907 – 13 November 1998) was a distinguished French stage and film actress.She was born Edwige Louise Caroline Cunatti to an Italian architect father and an Alsace-born mother. She was raised primarily in Dijon. In 1931 she married actor Pierre Feuillère, from whom she separated two years later (1933), but kept his surname. They had no children. She acted from 1931 until 1995.She died of natural causes, aged 91.
